AddressInfo.Title: Degerbyn Lanthandel - general store and gas station
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Charger outside general store on outer wall. Blue wall box near the gasoline pump. Type 2 contact.Pay-for charging.  InCharge app or RFID tag required for activation.

GeneralComments: Type 2 slot in wall box. The box does not give information about max current, however as a guideline a Nissan LEAF II charged approx. 2 kW/h in 30 minutes.
